name: τέρας n°3
description:
Third specimen of the Teratology collection.

Teratology, from ancient greec τέρας (téras, "sign sent by the gods, portent, marvel" and, in particular, "monster") and λογία (logía, "discourse, treaty, science, theory, or study").

Handmade collage on paper | 50 x 65 cm | 2021

2400 x 3200 px | 72 ppi
